+ * 
+ * This controller provides endpoints for:
+ * - Creating new questions
+ * - Updating existing questions
+ * - Retrieving questions by ID
+ * - Deleting questions
+ * - Getting all questions
+ * 
+ * @author Assessment Management System
+ * @version 1.0
+ */
+@RestController
